name: Double Dash Overtime!
description:
Double Dash Overtime Beta! This is a prototype that friends and I are currently working on.

Race against the clock to get out alive! Concept art will come soon! For now I'll be releasing builds for level design feedback. Please do leave as much feedback in the comments! Thank you.

If you enjoy the game, please donate! It fuels development!

For a changelog check here:

http://gamejolt.com/games/double-dash-overtime-bet...
